  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You and your eidolon’s attacks are infused with energy that manipulates life. When you use Tandem Boost’s @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-summoners-plus.misc.VucxKRn4BC9O3gCf]{synergy combo}, you can change the additional damage from precision damage to spirit, vitality, or void damage and the Strike gains the listed trait. In addition, when you critically succeed at a Strike while you have synergy, the target of your Strike is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{enfeebled 1} for 1 round. This enfeebled condition lasts for 2 rounds at 10th level, and for 3 rounds at 18th level.</p>"
    },
